Inputs and outputs

Controller: Passenger
Signals:
- destination
- estop

Controller: Safety Driver
Feedback:
- sight
- sound
Signals:
- steering
- brake
- accelerator
- estop

Controller: Autonomy
Inputs:
- destination
- estop
- map data
- sensor data

Controller: Vehicle Platform
Inputs:
- steering
- brake
- accelerator
Signals:
- actuators
Feedback:
- sensors